'''Facebook''' (nthawizina yofupikitsidwa kwa '''FB''' ) ndi malo [[Social networking service|ochezera a pa Intaneti]] ndi [[Website|webusaitiyi]] inayamba mu February 2004.  Linamangidwa ndi Mark Zuckerberg.  Lili ndi [[Facebook, Inc.]] {{Pomafika mu|September 2012}}   , Facebook ili ndi ogwiritsa ntchito oposa 1 biliyoni. Ogwiritsa ntchito akhoza kupanga [[Profile|mbiri yanu]] , kuwonjezera ena ogwiritsa ntchito ngati abwenzi, ndi kutumiza mauthenga.  Ogwiritsa ntchito Facebook ayenera [[Registration|kulemba]] asanayambe kugwiritsa ntchito tsamba.  Dzina la utumiki limachokera ku [[Facebook (directory)|dzina la buku]] lopatsidwa kwa ophunzira kumayambiriro kwa chaka cha sukulu ndi mayunivesite ena ku United States.  Mabuku awa amathandiza ophunzira kuti adziwane bwino.  Facebook imalola aliyense ogwiritsa ntchito omwe ali osachepera zaka 13 kuti azigwiritsa ntchito webusaitiyi. 

Facebook yakhazikitsidwa ndi [[Mark Zuckerberg]] ndi anzake ogwira nawo sukulu komanso ophunzira ena [[Computer science|a sayansi ya sayansi ya]] [[Eduardo Saverin]] , [[Dustin Moskovitz]] ndi [[Chris Hughes]] . Umembala wa webusaitiyi unali wa ophunzira a [[Harvard]] poyamba.  Kenaka zinaphatikizapo ma sukulu ena ku [[Boston]] , [[Ivy League]] , ndi [[Stanford University|University of Stanford]] .  Pomalizira pake anatsegulira ophunzira ku mayunivesite ena.  Pambuyo pake, idatseguka kwa ophunzira a sekondale, ndipo pomalizira pake, kwa aliyense wa zaka 13 ndi kupitirira.  Malingana ndi ConsumersReports.org mu May 2011, pali ana 7.5 miliyoni oposa 13 omwe ali ndi akaunti.  Izi zimaphwanya malamulo a webusaitiyi.  
[[File:Mark Zuckerberg (8137944472).jpg|thumb|Mwini wa facebook Mark Zuckerberg]]
A January 2009 [[Compete.com]] amaphunzira kuti Facebook ndi malo ogwiritsira ntchito [[Social networking service|malo ochezera a pa Intaneti]] pogwiritsa ntchito ogwiritsa ntchito pamwezi.  ''[[Entertainment Weekly|Zosangalatsa Masabata onse]]'' amaika malo kumapeto kwake kwa [[Decade|zaka khumi]] .  Ilo linati, "Pansi pa dziko lapansi ife timalankhula bwanji zochitika zathu, kukumbukira tsiku lakubadwa kwathu, ogwirizanitsa anzathu, ndi kusewera masewero a [[Lexulous|Scrabulous]] pamaso pa Facebook?"  [[Quantcast|Anthu]] akuganiza kuti Facebook ili ndi [[Quantcast|alendo]] okwana 138.9 miliyoni mwezi uliwonse mu May 2011.  Malingana ndi ''Social Media Today'' , mu April 2010 anthu okwana 41.6% a US anali ndi akaunti ya Facebook.   Kukula kwa Facebook kunayamba kuchepetsedwa m'madera ena.  Malowa anawonongeka ogwiritsa ntchito mamiliyoni 7 ku United States ndi Canada mu May 2011 poyerekezera ndi chiwerengero chakale.  

== Kudzudzula ==
Facebook yakhala ikukhudzidwa pazokangana zambiri [https://simple.wiktionary.org/wiki/privacy pazinsinsi]. Zina mwa zotsutsanazi zakhala zikukhudza anthu omwe akutha kuona mauthenga awo omwe anthu ena amawatumizira, ndipo ena ali pafupi makampani ndi [[Advertising|otsatsa]] akutha kuona mauthenga aumwini omwe akugwiritsa ntchito. 

Kafukufuku wofalitsidwa m'magazini ''[[PLOS ONE]]'' wasonyeza kuti Facebook ikhoza kuyambitsa kufalitsa chisangalalo pakati pa anthu komanso kusunga anthu.  Asayansi apeza kuti nthawi yochuluka imene anthu amagwiritsa ntchito pa Facebook patatha milungu iwiri, kenako iwo anamva. "Pamwamba, Facebook imapereka chithandizo chamtengo wapatali chokwaniritsa zofunika zaumunthu zogwirizana.  M'malo molimbikitsa ubwino, zotsatirazi zikusonyeza kuti Facebook ikhoza kuipitsa. "

